  <h2>Family Holiday in the Ith-Region</h2>
  <p>The Ith-Region is ideal for families with children – from theme parks to nature trails.</p>
  <h3>Top Family Activities</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Rasti-Land</strong> – Popular theme park with over 45 attractions for all ages</li>
    <li><strong>Ith-Sole Spa</strong> – Family pools, slides and sauna</li>
    <li><strong>Adventure Trails</strong> – Child-friendly hiking with interactive stations</li>
    <li><strong>Playgrounds</strong> – Nature-themed playgrounds in several villages</li>
    <li><strong>Farm Visits</strong> – Farms and wildlife parks in the region</li>
  </ul>
